HEADWORD: Kousso
<hw>Kous"so</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An
Abyssinian rosaceous tree (<spn>Brayera anthelmintica</spn>), the
flowers of which are used as a vermifuge.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>cusso</asp> and <asp>kosso</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

